OL,3,CMurder charge 20 years after man
OL,4,Cdisappeared on holiday
OL,6,FA man has been charged with the death
OL,7,Fof a British man who disappeared on
OL,8,Fholiday 20 years ago.
OL,10,FSteven Cook, from Sandbach, Cheshire,
OL,11,Fwas 20 when he disappeared from a
OL,12,Fholiday in Malia, Crete, in September
OL,13,F2005.
OL,15,FHis remains were discovered 12 years
OL,16,Flater, in 2017, at the bottom of a
OL,17,Fwell, but no further developments have
OL,18,Fever been made.
