OL,3,CMurder charge 20 years after man
OL,4,Cdisappeared on holiday
OL,6,FThe email, sent by the ex-wife of a
OL,7,FBritish man, 38, made a series of
OL,8,Fallegations towards her ex-husband,
OL,9,Fwho allegedly revealed the details of
OL,10,Fthe murder to her whilst under the
OL,11,Finfluence of drugs.
OL,13,FWhen the remains were discovered in
OL,14,F2017, the woman describes how her ex-
OL,15,Fhusband 'had a mental breakdown'.
OL,17,FThe 38-year-old man denies any
OL,18,Finvolvement.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
