OL,4,Cdisappeared on holiday
OL,6,FHe said: "There wont be any justice,
OL,7,Fapart from in a legal sense.
OL,9,F"There is no relief, it is just anger
OL,10,Ftowards an individual who chose to
OL,11,Ftake my brother's life.
OL,13,F"For so long they've lived without
OL,14,Fpunishment, and as a family we've been
OL,15,Fpunished in many ways.
OL,17,F"To this day I'm really struggling to
OL,18,Ftake phone calls that I'm not
OL,19,Fexpecting, because my heart just sinks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
