OL,3,CMurder charge 20 years after man
OL,4,Cdisappeared on holiday
OL,6,F"It's just purely natural instinct to
OL,7,Fgo back to the trauma that we've been
OL,8,Fthrough.
OL,10,F"I don't know a prison in the world
OL,11,Fthat would be as hellish as the prison
OL,12,Fwe'd been in for 12 years at the point
OL,13,Fthat my brother's body and remains
OL,14,Fwere found.
OL,16,F"We just want to let justice take its
OL,17,Fcourse and not get too involved unless
OL,18,Fwe have to."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
