OL,6,FThe case has been referred to the
OL,7,FMixed Jury Court of Heraklion, where a
OL,8,Fhearing will take place on 21 October.
OL,10,FIoannis Kostantoudakis, the lawyer who
OL,11,Frepresented Steven's family, said
OL,12,Funder Greek law the case could be
OL,13,Ftried without the suspect being
OL,14,Fphysically present, although the court
OL,15,Fcould order his presence if it felt
OL,16,Fnecessary.
